#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.116"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.116:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.116:0.2"
msgid "12. Kesivagga "
msgstr "12. With Kesi "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.116:0.3"
msgid "116. Appamādasutta "
msgstr "116. Diligence "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.116:1.1"
msgid "“Catūhi, bhikkhave, ṭhānehi appamādo karaṇīyo. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, you should be diligent in four situations. "

msgctxt "an4.116:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "an4.116:1.3"
msgid "Kāyaduccaritaṃ, bhikkhave, pajahatha, kāyasucaritaṃ bhāvetha; "
msgstr "Give up bad conduct by way of body, speech, and mind; and develop good conduct by way of body, speech, and mind. "

msgctxt "an4.116:1.4"
msgid "tattha ca mā pamādattha. "
msgstr "Don’t neglect these things. "

msgctxt "an4.116:1.5"
msgid "Vacīduccaritaṃ, bhikkhave, pajahatha, vacīsucaritaṃ bhāvetha; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.116:1.6"
msgid "tattha ca mā pamādattha. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.116:1.7"
msgid "Manoduccaritaṃ, bhikkhave, pajahatha, manosucaritaṃ bhāvetha; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.116:1.8"
msgid "tattha ca mā pamādattha. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.116:1.9"
msgid "Micchādiṭṭhiṃ, bhikkhave, pajahatha, sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāvetha; "
msgstr "Give up wrong view; and develop right view. "

msgctxt "an4.116:1.10"
msgid "tattha ca mā pamādattha. "
msgstr "Don’t neglect this. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.120, sc2
msgctxt "an4.116:2.1"
msgid "Yato kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno kāyaduccaritaṃ pahīnaṃ hoti kāyasucaritaṃ bhāvitaṃ, vacīduccaritaṃ pahīnaṃ hoti vacīsucaritaṃ bhāvitaṃ, manoduccaritaṃ pahīnaṃ hoti manosucaritaṃ bhāvitaṃ, micchādiṭṭhi pahīnā hoti sammādiṭṭhi bhāvitā, so na bhāyati samparāyikassa maraṇassā”ti. "
msgstr "A mendicant who has done these things does not fear death in lives to come.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.116:2.2"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
